      <thead>
        <tr><th>Difficulty</th><th>Level</th><th>Health</th><th>Base Damage</th><th>Resistances</th><th>Abilities</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Hell</td><td>110</td><td>120,000</td><td>215–275</td><td>Cold 100%, Fire 75%, Lightning 90%</td><td>Charged bolts, chilling aura, curse</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <h3>Lore</h3>
    <p>Uber Izual is a monstrous, corrupted spirit forged from the remains of the fallen angel. His relentless ice powers make him a nightmare to any adventurer unprepared for cold immunity.</p>
    <h3>Notable Drops</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Diablo's Horn (used in Pandemonium portal recipe)</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

<section id="uber-duriel">
