    <thead>
      <tr><th>Difficulty</th><th>Level</th><th>Health</th><th>Base Damage</th><th>Resistances</th><th>Abilities</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Hell</td><td>110</td><td>130,000</td><td>240–295</td><td>Cold 100%, Poison 100%, Fire 75%</td><td>Holy Freeze Aura, Poison nova, Charge</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <h3>Lore</h3>
  <p>Summoned through dark rituals, Uber Duriel retains his grotesque resilience and devastating charge. His icy aura slows even the most agile of adventurers, and his poison ensures no one walks away unscathed.</p>
  <h3>Notable Drops</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Baal's Eye (used in Pandemonium portal recipe)</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section id="uber-lilith">
  <h2>Uber Lilith (Mother of Deceit)</h2>
  <div class="images">
    <img src="images/uber_lilith_sprite.png" alt="Uber Lilith Classic Sprite">
    <img src="images/uber_lilith_render.png" alt="Uber Lilith D2R Render">
  </div>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Difficulty</th><th>Level</th><th>Health</th><th>Base Damage</th><th>Resistances</th><th>Abilities</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Hell</td><td>110</td><td>150,000</td><td>255–310</td><td>Poison 100%, Cold 75%, Fire 50%</td><td>Poison nova, shadow clone, life drain</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <h3>Lore</h3>
  <p>Uber Lilith is a twisted and powerful variant of Andariel, empowered by demonic rituals to become the Mother of Deceit. Her poison-laced claws and deceptive illusions can devastate even the strongest heroes.</p>
  <h3>Notable Drops</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Mephisto's Brain (used in Pandemonium portal recipe)</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section id="uber-tristram">
  <h2>Uber Tristram</h2>
  <p>Uber Tristram is the final battleground of the Pandemonium Event, where players face the ultimate challenge — the Uber versions of Mephisto, Diablo, and Baal simultaneously. Victory grants the powerful Hellfire Torch and earns a place among Sanctuary’s legends.</p>
</section>

