<h3>Ultimate Reward</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Hellfire Torch:</strong> +3 to random class skills, +10-20 to all attributes, +10-20 to all resistances, level 30 Hydra charges</li>
</ul>
</section>

<section id="diablo-clone">
  <h2>Diablo Clone (Uber Diablo)</h2>
  <div class="images">
    <img src="images/diablo_clone_sprite.png" alt="Diablo Clone Classic Sprite">
    <img src="images/diablo_clone_render.png" alt="Diablo Clone D2R Render">
  </div>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Difficulty</th><th>Level</th><th>Health</th><th>Base Damage</th><th>Resistances</th><th>Abilities</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Hell</td><td>110</td><td>640,000</td><td>380–460</td><td>Fire 100%, Lightning 75%, Cold 50%</td><td>Red lightning hose, firestorm, summon burning souls</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <h3>Lore</h3>
  <p>The Diablo Clone appears when the "World Event" is triggered by selling enough SoJs. He is an ultra-powerful form of Diablo with unique attacks and the only source of the Annihilus charm.</p>
  <h3>Notable Drops</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Annihilus:</strong> +1 to all skills, +10–20 to all stats, +10–20 to all resistances, +5–10% to experience gained</li>
  </ul>
